a little bit?

08:46.917 --> 08:49.224
You know?

08:49.267 --> 08:51.008
Yeah. Thanks.

08:51.052 --> 08:53.054
I'll, uh, you know,
I'll check back in with Ger.

08:53.097 --> 08:55.796
