08:55.839 --> 08:57.275
I'm not gonna...

08:57.319 --> 08:59.321
touch the banner.

08:59.364 --> 09:00.888
You know, your dad
should really bring

09:00.931 --> 09:02.454
the porn 'stache back.

09:02.498 --> 09:05.327
No. No. Um...Yes. [growls]

09:05.370 --> 09:08.635
Look, I, uh,
I don't mean to pry.

09:08.678 --> 09:11.028
Okay? And you just say the word,
I'll drop it completely.

09:11.072 --> 09:14.162
I don't know what happened
between you and your brother

09:14.205 --> 09:16.381
Ben, but I do know

09:16.425 --> 09:19.515
about brothers and trauma.

09:21.648 --> 09:23.606
Um, we were always close.

09:23.650 --> 09:25.086
Like, uh,

09:25.129 --> 09:28.132
"matching sweaters
at Christmas by choice"

09:28.176 --> 09:30.047
close.
Mm-hmm.

09:31.571 --> 09:33.790
And then...

09:33.834 --> 09:35.792
things happened.

09:35.836 --> 09:37.751
[inhales]

09:37.794 --> 09:39.753
Well, like you said,

09:39.796 --> 09:41.929
you-you have a brother.
You get it.

09:41.972 --> 09:43.626
I don't know
what things happened,

09:43.670 --> 09:45.759
or how Miles figures
into any of this,

09:45.802 --> 09:47.674
but what I can say is

09:47.717 --> 09:50.459
that when Emily died,

09:50.502 --> 09:52.722
I mean, Cordi disappeared.

09:52.766 --> 09:54.898
I mean, he was gone
gone, you know,

09:54.942 --> 09:57.553
and I went to him
when he was undercover,

09:57.597 --> 09:59.686
just to try and
get real with him

09:59.729 --> 10:01.383
'cause I was afraid
he-he would never come home.

10:01.426 --> 10:03.994
There was just this
world of hurt between us

10:04.038 --> 10:07.694
that would've
torn us apart, and...

10:07.737 --> 10:09.652
I may be totally off base,

10:09.696 --> 10:12.176
but I felt some of that

10:12.220 --> 10:14.178
with you two today.

10:14.222 --> 10:16.180
[sighs] Yeah.

10:16.224 --> 10:19.401
I just don't know what step
I'm supposed to take.

10:19.444 --> 10:22.099
I don't want to oversimplify it,
but, I mean, maybe just

10:22.143 --> 10:25.233
put one foot in front
of the other, you know?

10:25.276 --> 10:26.887
Repeat as necessary.

10:26.930 --> 10:29.585
See where that road
takes you.

10:29.629 --> 10:32.240
It's got to be a lot better than
where you two are right now.

10:34.851 --> 10:37.898
So, we ditching
homeroom or...[laughing]

10:37.941 --> 10:39.203
...got a big game,
varsity?

10:39.247 --> 10:41.815
No, no, I-I just
wanted to, uh,

10:41.858 --> 10:43.599
copy your and
Em's homework

10:43.643 --> 10:45.470
under the bleachers
before biology.

10:45.514 --> 10:47.472
Oh, memories.

10:47.516 --> 10:48.473
Yeah, that's kind of

10:48.517 --> 10:49.866
why I wanted to

10:49.910 --> 10:52.347
see you here.
Memories, you know?

10:52.390 --> 10:53.348
Simpler times.

10:53.391 --> 10:55.698
Uh...

10:55.742 --> 10:57.047
At the Kansas show,

10:57.091 --> 10:58.483
I didn't mean to step
in between you

10:58.527 --> 11:00.529
and-and your new-- you...

11:00.572 --> 11:02.574
I didn't mean to step
in between you and Gale.[cell phone ringing]

11:02.618 --> 11:04.794
But I did. Sorry.No, it's-it's fine.

11:04.838 --> 11:06.709
Why don't you...
Might be work, so...No, no, no. I-I-I

11:06.753 --> 11:08.668
feel terrible about
the way I acted.

11:08.711 --> 11:10.234
And I know
that-that's not

11:10.278 --> 11:13.585
the reason we're-we're
not... you know, together,

11:13.629 --> 11:15.849
but I-I-I needed
to-to-to own up to it,

11:15.892 --> 11:19.069
and I need
to make it...

11:19.113 --> 11:20.070
right.

11:20.114 --> 11:22.594
Um...

11:22.638 --> 11:23.987
Geri,

11:24.031 --> 11:26.947
I-I'm gonna show you
that I'm committed to

11:26.990 --> 11:29.166
our friendship

11:29.210 --> 11:31.734
because that's still there,
always will be.

11:31.778 --> 11:34.868
I know that.

11:34.911 --> 11:36.608
So, you-your big ask?

11:36.652 --> 11:38.045
[cell phone ringing]You-you...

11:38.088 --> 11:39.350
I mean, you texted me...Right, yeah, yeah, yeah.

11:39.394 --> 11:41.744
Uh, sorry, um,
it-it's-it's not for me,

11:41.788 --> 11:43.224
it's-it's for,
it's for my folks.

11:43.267 --> 11:45.748
Uh, so we're throwing
